{
  "texts": [
    "This method involves evaluating the model performance across multiple categories of the data.",
    "As a case study, S1 applied the slicing approach to explore the gender-based differences in MOOC dropout prediction models.",
    "The study proposed a new fairness metric, ABROCA, the Absolute Between-ROC Area.",
    "This metric measures the absolute value of the area between the baseline group ROC curve ROCb and the comparison group(s) ROCc.",
    "The lower the ABROCA value, the less unfair the algorithm."
  ]
}